## Diagnostic Checklist

```
Focus lost on every keystroke?
│
├── Is a component defined inside another component's body?  → Move it outside
├── Is a component defined inside a render prop or callback? → Extract it
├── Is a key prop changing on the input?                     → Fix the key
└── Is a parent conditionally wrapping the input?           → Check render tree stability
```

